          "TITLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "A study of excitation functions for some residues",
                "produced in the system 14-N+128-Te in the energy range",
                " 64-90 MeV"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "REFERENCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "code": "J,IMP/E,14,775,2005",
                "code_unit": [
                  {
                    "unit": "J,IMP/E,14,775,2005",
                    "doi": "10.1142/S0218301305003545",
                    "field": {
                      "reference_type": "J",
                      "reference": {
                        "code": "IMP/E",
                        "number": null,
                        "volume": "14",
                        "part": null,
                        "issue": null,
                        "page": "775"
                      },
                      "date": 2005
                    }
                  }
                ],
                "unit_combination": "(%)"
              },
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "AUTHOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "Unnati",
                "Manoj Kumar Sharma",
                "B.P.Singh",
                "R.Prasad",
                "Sunita Gupta",
                "H.D.Bhardwaj",
                "A.K.Sinha"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "INSTITUTE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "3INDMUA"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Department of physics,"
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "3INDIND"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Department of physics, Agra college, Agra,",
                " department of physics, DSN college, UNNAO, and",
                " IUC-DAEF, Calcutta centre."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Samples of 128-Te of thickness 0.92 mg/cm2 were",
                "prepared from the enriched isotope of 128-Te (87%) by",
                "vacuum evaporation on aluminum foils of thickness 6.75",
                "mg/cm2.  The thickness of the samples was determined by",
                "measuring the energy loss of 5.485 MeV alpha-particles",
                "from a 241-Am source while passing through the target.",
                "The samples were fixed on aluminum holders of size",
                "1.2*1.2 cm2 with concentric circular holes of 10 mm",
                "diameter at their centers."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "MONITOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": null,
                "reaction": {
                  "code": "52-TE-128(7-N-14,EL)52-TE-128,,DA",
                  "code_unit": [
                    {
                      "unit": "52-TE-128(7-N-14,EL)52-TE-128,,DA",
                      "field": {
                        "reaction": "52-TE-128(7-N-14,EL)52-TE-128",
                        "target": "52-TE-128",
                        "projectile": "7-N-14",
                        "process": "EL",
                        "product": "52-TE-128",
                        "quantity": ",DA",
                        "data_type": null,
                        "general_quantity_modifier": null,
                        "quantity_236": ",DA"
                      }
                    }
                  ],
                  "unit_combination": "(%)"
                }
              },
              "free_text": [
                "",
                "The two detectors (rutherford monitors) were kept at",
                "30 degrees with respect to the direction of the beam at",
                "the forward angle to record the scattered incident ions",
                "for flux normalization."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "HPGE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " To measure gamma-spectra."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SIBAR"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Rutherford monitor."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "FACILITY": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "facility": [
                  "VDGT"
                ],
                "institute": "3INDNSD"
              },
              "free_text": [
                " 14-UD pelletron"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SITA"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Six samples of 128-Te were irradiated",
                "individually."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "EXTB"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "  A 14-N (5+/6+) beam at energies 64, 71, 76, 81,",
                "86 and 90 MeV. The beam currents of 5-particle",
                "nanoamperes were employed for irradiation."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "BCINT"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The incident flux was also determined from the",
                "total charge collected in the faraday cup."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "ACTIV"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The duration of each irradiation was kept at ~3",
                "hours."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "GSPEC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " In order to measure short-lived activities,",
                "samples were quickly taken out from the scattering",
                "chamber using the in-vacuum transfer facility.  The",
                "sample-detector separation was suitably adjusted so as",
                "to keep the dead time <5%.  The counting of irradiated",
                "samples was performed for several days."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "-By authors.  The flux of the incident beam determined",
                "from the counts of the rutherford monitors and from the",
                "integrated current counts of the faraday cup were found",
                "to agree with each other within 5%."
              ]
            }
          ],
