                "heading": "ERR-T",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The overall uncertainties in the measured",
                "cross-sections includes:",
                "1. The  uncertainty  in  determining",
